                <note rend="inline" type="source">893.51/3955: Telegram</note>
                <head>
                    <hi rend="italic">The <gloss type="from">Acting Secretary of State</gloss> to
                        the Minister in China</hi> (<persName type="to">
                        <hi rend="italic">Schurman</hi>
                    </persName>)</head>
                <opener>
                    <dateline rendition="#right">
                        <placeName>
                            <hi rend="smallcaps">Washington</hi>
                        </placeName>, <date calendar="gregorian" when="1922-09-01T17:00:00-04:00">
                            <hi rend="italic">September 1, 1922—5 p.m.</hi>
                        </date>
                    </dateline>
                </opener>
                <p>209. Your 353, August 29, 1 p.m.</p>
                <p>Department fails to understand why Chinese Government is able to pay $600,000
                    interest on loan mentioned and does not make an interest payment on the several
                    defaulted American obligations. You may so inform Chinese Government.</p>
                <closer>
                    <signed>
                        <hi rend="smallcaps">Phillips</hi>
                    </signed>
                </closer>
            </div>
        </body>
    </text>
